 *
 * The conclusion is that difference should be signed and comparison
 * operators should be avoided. Instead compare with difference to 
 * handle wrap-around and negative interval correctly.
 *   uint32_t t0, t1;
 *   int32_t diff = t1 - t0;
 *   bool wrong1 = t1 < t0; 
